We may also collect information about you from third parties, such as when others give us your information (e.g., to invite you to use the Services), from data enrichment services (e.g., to better tailor our communications to you), or when you link your Account (as defined in the Terms of Service) to third party services (e.g., when you link your email account to upload your contacts). We will only use information collected from third parties for the specific reason for which it was provided to us and for no other purpose.
Device Information ‚Äì we may also collect information collected automatically about your device and your usage of the Services (‚ÄúDevice Information‚Äù), such as IP address, browser type, referring/exit pages, and operating system.
We use Account Information and Device Information we collect for the following purposes only:
Creating and administering your Account.
Providing you with the Services.
Improving and modifying the Services, such as by designing or customizing existing and future offerings to your preferences.
Tracking the performance of our Services and your usage of our Services, in order to improve our Services for your benefit.
Understanding how you and other users discovered our Services, including from advertisements for our Services that we show on third party websites, apps, mailing lists and other third party properties. This includes the ability to track if you and other users choose to purchase anything in our Services. (Please see the ‚ÄúCookies and Other Tracking Technologies‚Äù section, below, for more information on this point.)
