to ensure the safety and stability of the Services (such as by removing User Content that may be crashing our servers);
to train and improve our algorithms and models for purposes of improving the Services (such as by helping our Services better identify individuals in User Content), but only where you explicitly consent to this use;
to respond to your requests and inquiries (such as during a customer support inquiry).
